Backend:

Node.js with Express: Server-side framework.
Socket.io: Real-time bidirectional communication.
Kafka-node or kafkajs: Kafka client for Node.js.
Redis: In-memory data store for caching and presence.

Message Brokering:

Apache Kafka: Distributed streaming platform.

Frontend:

React.js: Frontend library for building user interfaces.


Other Tools:

Docker: Containerization for deployment.
Docker Compose: Orchestrating multi-container Docker applications.


scalable-chat-app/
├── src/
│   ├── consumers/
│   │   └── messageConsumer.js
│   ├── producers/
